<sup>,</sup>
<a href="#ref46" class="usa-link" aria-describedby="ref46"><sup>46</sup></a> Another three studies reported that targeted sample size was not reached.<a href="#ref4" class="usa-link" aria-describedby="ref4"><sup>4</sup></a>
<sup>,</sup>
